370
00:23:28.115 --> 00:23:30.909
Our Deputy Bong lost big time. right?

371
00:23:30.992 --> 00:23:32.994
So they'll have the enforcers
come after you.

372
00:23:33.078 --> 00:23:34.538
We catch those guys

373
00:23:35.664 --> 00:23:38.917
