397
00:25:34.407 --> 00:25:35.617
Hurry up.

398
00:25:35.700 --> 00:25:38.119
Just fucking hand them over!

399
00:25:41.164 --> 00:25:42.165
Hey.

400
00:25:42.666 --> 00:25:43.708
I said hand it over.

