402
00:25:47.045 --> 00:25:48.838
-It's not working.
-Give it here.

403
00:25:56.513 --> 00:25:57.514
-Oh no.
-Damn it.

404
00:25:57.597 --> 00:25:59.140
-I'm sorry.
-Fucking hell.

405
00:25:59.224 --> 00:26:00.350
For fuck's sake.

406
00:26:00.850 --> 00:26:02.102
Oh no.

407
00:26:02.602 --> 00:26:03.979
My phone

408
00:26:05.105 --> 00:26:06.982
