409
00:26:07.065 --> 00:26:10.277
For fuck's sake.
You're a real piece of work.

410
00:26:10.860 --> 00:26:12.320
I'm sorry.

411
00:26:23.290 --> 00:26:27.794
INSPECTOR IM HAN-RIM

