430
00:27:48.875 --> 00:27:50.210
-No. I can't.
-Get out. moron.

431
00:27:50.293 --> 00:27:51.378
-I can't.
-Get out.

432
00:27:51.461 --> 00:27:53.088
-Get the fuck out.
-I really can't.

433
00:27:53.171 --> 00:27:55.632
-I said get the fuck out.
-No. I really can't do it.

434
00:27:55.715 --> 00:27:57.467
For fuck's sake.

435
00:28:07.560 --> 00:28:08.687
-You little shit.
-What…

436
00:28:09.562 --> 00:28:10.980
