468
00:29:53.875 --> 00:29:55.168
-Damn it.
-I'm sorry!

469
00:29:56.211 --> 00:29:58.254
-Get your act together.
-Yes. bro!

470
00:29:59.130 --> 00:30:01.216
Fucking morons.

471
00:30:01.299 --> 00:30:02.884
