473
00:30:05.303 --> 00:30:06.971
Train him and get him started.

474
00:30:07.055 --> 00:30:08.515
Yes. bro!

475
00:30:09.933 --> 00:30:11.267
Fucking follow me.

476
00:30:12.393 --> 00:30:14.979
