477
00:30:15.063 --> 00:30:17.398
-For fuck's sake. Come with me.
-Wait…

478
00:30:23.947 --> 00:30:25.073
-Sit.
-Sorry?

479
00:30:25.156 --> 00:30:26.533
-I said sit.
-Right.

480
00:30:27.408 --> 00:30:28.368
Okay.

481
00:30:28.451 --> 00:30:31.037
