501
00:31:48.656 --> 00:31:49.699
50.000 WON BONUS

502
00:31:49.782 --> 00:31:51.200
MESSAGE HAS BEEN SENT

503
00:31:51.284 --> 00:31:54.787
Get the hell out. goddamn dumbasses.
You fucking morons.

504
00:31:54.871 --> 00:31:57.582
You're fucking useless.
